# Enterprise Dashboard Automation (Portfolio)

A Python-based test automation project focused on validating dashboard behavior,
record workflows, and data exports in a modern web application.

This repository is intentionally designed as a **portfolio example** showcasing
UI and API test automation using **pytest** and **Playwright**, with organized
test suites and reusable helper utilities.

> **Note**  
> Product names, UI labels, workflows, and helpers have been anonymized to remove
> proprietary or sensitive details while preserving real-world testing patterns.

---

## Overview

The project demonstrates automation coverage across multiple functional areas:

### Dashboard validation
- Default dashboard layout
- Summary metric widgets
- Entity-level cards
- Section/widget visibility and consistency

### Record workflow validation
- Default and advanced filters
- Record list behavior
- Record detail navigation
- Status-based workflows (e.g., dismiss / restore actions)

### Analytics / performance validation
- Landing behavior
- Default field values
- Page-level expectations

### API / export validation
- Export header structure
- Data-driven validation scenarios
- UI-to-export consistency checks

---

## Tech stack

- Python 3.12
- pytest
- Playwright
- Allure-compatible reporting
